- How to view the status area (bottom half of the screen)

                          Desperado's lateral speed
                                    |
 +------------------------+--------------------+
 | SCORE 000000           +--------------------+
 | ENEMY 32               |       Radar        |
 | DESPERADO 3            |    (see below)     |
 +------------------------+--------------------+
 +---------------------------------------------+
                  |
Planet Bester's nuclear shield gauge (decreases dramatically when the basin falls)

 SCORE ------- The current score.
               Points are added when you defeat enemy characters or clear stages.
 ENEMY ------- This is the number of enemy characters you must defeat on this level.
               When it reaches 0, the level is cleared.
 DESPERADO --- The remaining number of your own ships.
               The time you are currently playing does not count.

If the nuclear shield reaches 0, the game is over.
It will recover when the surface is cleared.

How to read the radar:

 +------------------------------+
 |              .        .      | Red dot (inside the small frame)... Your ship (Desperado)
 |     .  .      +---+       .  | White dots (lots)               ... enemy aircraft
 | .             | . |   .      | Light blue dot (one)            ... Antimatter bomb "Tub"
 |               +---+     .    |
 +------------------------------+
                  |
The contents of the small frame will be displayed on the game screen.
